  "text": "This is pivotal to the correct operation of the R-D optimization algorithm. Chou [CITATION_1] considers sample distortion to be additive, that is, the overall distortion is a large initial value less the sum of reductions in distortion due to receiving a set of L packets. This is described in (1).",
